{"tid":857193,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇excel達人？","createTime":"2018-10-11T03:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:25:48.000Z","uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"261cc3dfd4743f766c9cb1f95fbf3ed719ef7ca8","tid":857193,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:22:08.000Z","msg":"一個list(A2:A15)入面有一堆data<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShC0bMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShC0bMz.png&h=8f71c8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想搵list入面所有unique item(至少出現過一次，即係C2:C5)<br />\ngoogle過有好多唔同方法，但都只係搵已知嘅item<br />\n但我個list入面d data每次都唔同，可能下一次係:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZ64DtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZ64DtQ.png&h=2d80071a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇方法每次都return到唔同data嘅unique item<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nformula同VBA版都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b31b1b2803a5822eeda0c823ad39a67d8c4fb5","tid":857193,"uid":150568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"Formula: remove duplicate (alt+a+m)"},{"pid":"c971e280e0a8533d43268c573b8d77b4d6591ef5","tid":857193,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"弱智既做法：<br />\n<br />\nColumn B 比個value 1<br />\n<br />\n跟住insert 張pivot table<br />\n<br />\nSummary item 大過1既就係你想要既item"},{"pid":"afc0afc1facc5956b457846956de5aef2d7da487","tid":857193,"uid":37623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"用vlookup"},{"pid":"2f14bc489b1433e771a4226eca6db148aa854c77","tid":857193,"uid":34047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"copy column a<br />\npaste column c<br />\npress remove duplicate<br />\n搞掂"},{"pid":"b69eca061e49d223da7feab6306fb369b3b2fc26","tid":857193,"ui