lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原來咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有樣野想問<br />\n平時一個cell入面有句子想reference其他cell value, 可以好簡單咁用&quot;&quot;同&amp;:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HRz5ty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HRz5ty.png&h=c0fe6ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但如果想reference嘅cell嘅數量每次都唔同(少咗or多咗)，可以點做？<br />\neg1. (想reference嘅cell少咗, E2 output多咗個逗號)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvMz5vv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvMz5vv.png&h=f37d1d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\neg2. (想reference嘅cell多咗, E2 output少咗grape)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mj7oepb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMj7oepb.png&h=1cf29146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n需唔需要做logic test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nformula同vba版都想知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:50:42.000Z","msg":"咁你咪用vba數下有幾多個item lor<br />\n跟住加個for loop咪可以將生果名稱擺埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n你試下下面依段code。<br />\nColumn A果part我無寫到，純粹寫咗由Column C至Column E。<br />\n我Excel都係自學，唔知咁樣寫法算唔算蠢，不過至少係work。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">Sub test()\nDim item As Integer\nDim FruitName As String\n\nitem = WorksheetFunction.CountA(Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Range(&quot;C2:C10&quot;)) '計算C2至C10有幾多種生果\n\nFor i = 1 To item\n    If i = 1 Then\n        FruitName = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i + 1, 3) '第一款生果\n    Else\n        FruitName = FruitName &amp; &quot;, &quot; &amp; Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i + 1, 3) '由第二款生果開始，前面要有comma同space\n    End If\n        \nNext i\n\nWorksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(2, 5) = &quot;Fruits: &quot; &amp; FruitName '在E2顯示結果\n\nEnd Sub\n\n</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7599b34841a7770ab8da4bde13d3bbbc73a21fe4","tid":857193,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc65083b9259ef165e9398c7e4146cc4f123343c","tid":857193,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7599b34841a7770ab8da4bde13d3bbbc73a21fe4","tid":857193,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f532f678cae4f95cd1f6dcc4e09e6cbcdd873b3","tid":857193,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"101108235bf96b56ea7cac20ce12dcabfb4d01c0","tid":857193,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原來咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有樣野想問<br />\n平時一個cell入面有句子想reference其他cell value, 可以好簡單咁用&quot;&quot;同&amp;:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HRz5ty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HRz5ty.png&h=c0fe6ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但如果想reference嘅cell嘅數量每次都唔同(少咗or多咗)，可以點做？<br />\neg1. (想reference嘅cell少咗, E2 output多咗個逗號)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvMz5vv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvMz5vv.png&h=f37d1d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\neg2. (想reference嘅cell多咗, E2 output少咗grape)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mj7oepb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMj7oepb.png&h=1cf29146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n需唔需要做logic test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nformula同vba版都想知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:50:42.000Z","msg":"咁你咪用vba數下有幾多個item lor<br />\n跟住加個for loop咪可以將生果名稱擺埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n你試下下面依段code。<br />\nColumn A果part我無寫到，純粹寫咗由Column C至Column E。<br />\n我Excel都係自學，唔知咁樣寫法算唔算蠢，不過至少係work。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">Sub test()\nDim item As Integer\nDim FruitName As String\n\nitem = WorksheetFunction.CountA(Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Range(&quot;C2:C10&quot;)) '計算C2至C10有幾多種生果\n\nFor i = 1 To item\n    If i = 1 Then\n        FruitName = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i + 1, 3) '第一款生果\n    Else\n        FruitName = FruitName &amp; &quot;, &quot; &amp; Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i + 1, 3) '由第二款生果開始，前面要有comma同space\n    End If\n        \nNext i\n\nWorksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(2, 5) = &quot;Fruits: &quot; &amp; FruitName '在E2顯示結果\n\nEnd Sub\n\n</code></pre>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"一兩分鐘寫完啦"},{"pid":"03f8423bf8f9f437dba976fa997f25720542c401","tid":857193,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed8df289d89d960d1fcac9b87704bca275db8fcf","tid":857193,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f8423bf8f9f437dba976fa997f25720542c401","tid":857193,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc65083b9259ef165e9398c7e4146cc4f123343c","tid":857193,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7599b34841a7770ab8da4bde13d3bbbc73a21fe4","tid":857193,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"一兩分鐘寫完啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"一個for loop加一個if你想幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5463083aa3fed1e0bad00eee3c884e9edbd6301c","tid":857193,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6d7d9f846b573b4e91db07784989a3d87360b24","tid":857193,"uid":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f532f678cae4f95cd1f6dcc4e09e6cbcdd873